I think you've made a bit of mixing magic.  I was really worried just reading the recipe.   That's a lot of Jam and INW raspberry.  But wow.  On a  SNV,  you can taste the blueberries fighting the raspberry for dominance on the inhale.  On the finish it really does come to together as a blue raspberry jolly rancher.  Its magical.&#xD;
&#xD;
Can't wait till I see how this steeps out!  Hope it gets better!
